OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779437195
OL,3,CIran's World Cup team applies for US
OL,4,Cvisas in Turkey
OL,6,FSome of the Iranian squad arrived at
OL,7,Fthe embassy on Thursday morning
OL,9,FMembers of the Iranian football team
OL,10,Fhave applied for visas to enter the
OL,11,FUnited States ahead of the World Cup
OL,12,Fnext month.
OL,14,FThe tournament is being hosted by the
OL,15,FUS, Mexico and Canada, but all three
OL,16,Fof Iran's scheduled games are due to
OL,17,Fbe held in the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
