CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779437195
OL,3,CIran's World Cup team applies for US
OL,4,Cvisas in Turkey
OL,6,FDespite the ongoing conflict between
OL,7,Fboth sides, the US rejected calls to
OL,8,Fmove the games to one of the other
OL,9,Fhost countries.
OL,11,FIran has insisted its team will take
OL,12,Fpart in the tournament, despite the
OL,13,Fwar.
OL,15,FOn Thursday, players Omid Noorafkhan,
OL,16,FSeyed Hossein Hossein, Ehsan Hajsafi
OL,17,Fand Aria Yousefi were seen entering
OL,18,Fand leaving the US embassy in Ankara,
OL,19,FTurkey, to make their visa
OL,20,Fapplications.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779437195
OL,3,CIran's World Cup team applies for US
OL,4,Cvisas in Turkey
OL,6,FITV News understands the embassy will
OL,7,Fapprove the applications.
OL,9,FThe players declined to answer
OL,10,Fquestions from gathered media when
OL,11,Fthey arrived and later left the
OL,12,Fembassy.
OL,14,FIt is understood the players also
OL,15,Fplanned to submit a similar
OL,16,Fapplication to the Canadian embassy on
OL,17,FThursday.
OL,19,FThe Iranian team arrived in Turkey on
OL,20,FMonday as part of a training camp
OL,21,Fahead of travelling to the US in June.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
