OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779437195
OL,3,CIran's World Cup team applies for US
OL,4,Cvisas in Turkey
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIran and the US have not had
OL,12,Fdiplomatic ties since the 1980s. Iran
OL,13,Fhas a history of detaining any
OL,14,FAmerican citizen who enters its
OL,15,Fborders, and the US also views harshly
OL,16,Fanyone hoping to enter the US who has
OL,17,Fpreviously visited Iran.
OL,19,FIran's delegation is expected to
OL,20,Farrive at a training base in Tucson,
OL,21,FArizona, between June 5 and June 10.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
