CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779437195
OL,3,CIran's World Cup team applies for US
OL,4,Cvisas in Turkey
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump's
OL,7,Fadministration promised in January to
OL,8,Fgive athletes and coaches visiting for
OL,9,Fmajor sporting events an exemption
OL,10,Ffrom travel bans, but not other
OL,11,Fofficials.
OL,13,FIran has been drawn in Group G and
OL,14,Fwill open their campaign against New
OL,15,FZealand in Los Angeles on June 15.
OL,17,FThey will then face Belgium and Egypt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
